  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810580/extras/b64cd1cb476a76d608d819fcbacd49b8.avif?t=1711386976\" width=640 height=82 /></span><br><br><strong><u>There's Something In The Ice</u></strong> is a first-person horror game.<br><br><strong>Plot:</strong><br>In 2015, three scientists at the Antarctic research station Zarya drilled into the ice to a depth of 2 kilometers and took samples to study...<br>As they were returning to base, a severe snowstorm began.<br>Arriving at the base, the scientists went down to the old bunker, as the security protocol told them, to wait it out...<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There is not a single note in the game. The plot is presented through dialogues with characters.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Realistic graphics.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Advanced lighting system LUMEN (Unreal Engine 5).</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Atmosphere inspired by the movie \"The Thing\" and other sci-fi films and games.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810580/extras/b64cd1cb476a76d608d819fcbacd49b8.avif?t=1711386976\" width=640 height=82 /></span><br><br><strong><u>There's Something In The Ice</u></strong> is a first-person horror game.<br><br><strong>Plot:</strong><br>In 2015, three scientists at the Antarctic research station Zarya drilled into the ice to a depth of 2 kilometers and took samples to study...<br>As they were returning to base, a severe snowstorm began.<br>Arriving at the base, the scientists went down to the old bunker, as the security protocol told them, to wait it out...<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There is not a single note in the game. The plot is presented through dialogues with characters.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Realistic graphics.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Advanced lighting system LUMEN (Unreal Engine 5).</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Atmosphere inspired by the movie \"The Thing\" and other sci-fi films and games.</li></ul>",
